---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="BridgeAIChat Claude Guide">
  <section class="card">
    <div class="eyebrow">Tool Guide</div>
    <h1>Claude</h1>
    <p>Claude remains supported, but local auth and quota state on the device controls whether it can answer.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Ensure the device is logged into Claude CLI.</li>
      <li>Quota exhaustion will prevent successful replies.</li>
      <li>Documented as supported with caveats in the first beta.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
